@Node Description "Description"

  Description
  ===========

    This door creates stats for each user.

    It currently creates the following files:

    HBBS:System/Data/Users/<userid>/ConfStats.CFG

@EndNode

@Node Installation "Installation"

  Installation
  ============

    The door is stored as:

    HBBS:Doors/System/StatsGenerator/StatsGenerator.HBBS

    This is included and enabled with a fresh installation of HydraBBS
    since V1.11.  Users of prior version should do this:

    Add the following lines to a Commands/System file (HBBS:Commands/System is
    recommended).

    StatsGenerator_Type_1=HBBS
    StatsGenerator_Door_1=HBBS:Doors/System/StatsGenerator/StatsGenerator.HBBS {N} {O}

@EndNode

